<table summary="This table lists the pages with budget intiative changes for the 31 July 2000 release with details of the change"><caption>Budget Initiative</caption>
<thead><tr><th scope="col">Topic No.</th>
<th scope="col">Details</th>
</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1.1.A.30</td>
<td>
<p>Delete whole section.</p>
<p>Add note See 1.1.P.510.</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td>1.1.M.150</td>
<td>Inclusion of Calvary Chapel, Perth (pastors) and River of Life Australia (all pastors).</td>
